item.title: Don't Miss Out on the Incredible Homes on Display at the Parade of Homes in Wichita, KS!
item.description: Introduction to the Parade of Homes in Wichita, KS Are you thinking of building or remodeling your home in Wichita, KS? If so, you won’t want to miss out on the incredible homes featured in the Parade of Homes The Parade of Homes is an annual event showcasing the latest and greatest in home building and remodeling It is a great opportunity to get inspired and see the latest trends in home design
